long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Have you ever jumped between magiceden and rarity in order to see the rarity of an NFT? Rejoice! With this extension installed you won't have to do that. We're constantly updating our api to match the data and you can stay on magiceden while knowing the rarity of each item in the collection.
